description.en:
I&rsquo;ve transmigrated into the world of the BL webtoon &lt;In The House of Dolls, There&rsquo;s Another Doll Living There&gt; where I left my one and only spiteful comment. On top of that, I become the adopted younger sister of my favorite character: the obsessive male lead who is later regretful for his actions, but still dies along with the duke in the end. So, I was determined. Since I have transmigrated into this world, I can&rsquo;t stand by and watch my favorite character die. Additionally, I also don&rsquo;t want to die. That&rsquo;s why, author, I'll need to change the tags and the ending of this webtoon slightly! From &lt;Obsessive Male lead&gt; to &lt;Considerate Male Lead&gt;. From &lt;Sad Ending&gt; to &lt;Happy Ending&gt;. 

&ldquo;Brother, please smile like that in front of others as well.&rdquo; I said to Lucian, who doesn&rsquo;t smile even a little bit in front of others. 
&ldquo;&hellip;&rdquo;

Was that request too out of the blue?
Lucian looked at me with a peculiar expression. 
&ldquo;If you do that, I will give you a gift.&rdquo;
I said that because I wanted to help him in anyway I could. 

He looked at me for a bit and hesitated before replying, &ldquo;A gift&hellip; Is anything fine?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Of course!&rdquo;
The moment I gave that answer with certainty, his expression changed right at once to that of a starving predator... Did I make mistake?
Then, Lucian calmly replied with an expression full of expectation. 

&ldquo;Give yourself to me, Rachel.&rdquo;
Huh? What did he say? What did he just ask for?
